{"tid":2458203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天文台：暫難預測今年會否有超強颱風　籲市民做好準備","createTime":"2021-03-23T08:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T07:34:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":14,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"25bd1a942d0f87b4659c1e2ab45e6b3c76e4742d","tid":2458203,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:50:33.000Z","msg":"天文台台長鄭楚明表示，受疫情影響，去年經濟活動減少，但二氧化碳累積濃度仍創新高，預料二氧化碳濃度上升的趨勢仍然存在。<br />\n<br />\n鄭楚明說，受到全球暖化影響，下雨時雨勢可能會較大。他表示，本港平均一年的熱帶氣旋數目為4至7個，今年就預計有5至8個，屬正常至偏多。他又說，目前難以預測會否出現如超強颱風山竹的強度，認為市民應做好準備，應對一旦出現的極端天氣。<br />\n<br />\n另外，天文台今日下午開始，在9天天氣預報中，會加入「顯著降雨概率」預報，即提供香港廣泛地區累積雨量達10毫米或以上的預測概率，亦計劃第二季起推出「局部地區大雨提示」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582110-20210323.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582110-20210323.htm&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97Rzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=489bc49f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582110-20210323.htm&h=1baa37fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582110-20210323.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1c60205825b9baa6e36ad3580a4ae58d62ec5b5f","tid":2458203,"uid":76804,"like":236,"dislike":9,"score":227,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:51:19.000Z","msg":"幾勁既天災<br />\n都及唔上宜家經歷緊既人禍"},{"pid":"6a0d316eb5a5f8d0bee388951ddeb6d4e52b65bc","tid":2458203,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823f4adc1e84f525bbe5d2d57c1f379b8883b2af","tid":2458203,"uid":128102,"like":112,"dislike":3,"score":109,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xDoBwec.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxDoBwec.gif&h=1089cddb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8fc642825e93ac01125dd52f6d7067b69d78852","tid":2458203,"uid":14