ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:47:05.000Z","msg":"收到消息今年颱風會有0-50個"},{"pid":"ce884c8fc84015d8fa28e27a1786bf5c161c4985","tid":2458203,"uid":244612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25bd1a942d0f87b4659c1e2ab45e6b3c76e4742d","tid":2458203,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:50:33.000Z","msg":"天文台台長鄭楚明表示，受疫情影響，去年經濟活動減少，但二氧化碳累積濃度仍創新高，預料二氧化碳濃度上升的趨勢仍然存在。<br />\n<br />\n鄭楚明說，受到全球暖化影響，下雨時雨勢可能會較大。他表示，本港平均一年的熱帶氣旋數目為4至7個，今年就預計有5至8個，屬正常至偏多。他又說，目前難以預測會否出現如超強颱風山竹的強度，認為市民應做好準備，應對一旦出現的極端天氣。<br />\n<br />\n另外，天文台今日下午開始，在9天天氣預報中，會加入「顯著降雨概率」預報，即提供香港廣泛地區累積雨量達10毫米或以上的預測概率，亦計劃第二季起推出「局部地區大雨提示」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582110-20210323.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582110-20210323.htm&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97Rzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=489bc49f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582110-20210323.htm&h=1baa37fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582110-20210323.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />年年都咁講架啦"},{"pid":"d2c3151d359d4c35293901025758ed7b0fee80ca","tid":2458203,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:49:41.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，成日想掛8號阻我返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3583cd3264f9b3b3c92edeca7445a98556df99","tid":2458203,"uid":154429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"850dbf5bdce791df6632c34ecfadbd74f3603ce9","tid":2458203,"uid":58604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"186363d925c602b6dd0af0005bb163deb79b833f","tid":2458203,"uid":154429,"like":1,"dislike